Subject: [PATCH] powerpc/book3s64/pkeys: Simplify the key initialization

References: jsc#SLE-16556 bsc#1078248 FATE#322447
Patch-mainline: v5.9-rc1
Git-commit: f491fe3fb41eafc7a159874040e032ad41ade210

Add documentation explaining the execute_only_key. The reservation and initialization mask
